  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pakistan floods kill 176 people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese Foreign Minister Wang Yi said he was shocked to learn that the floods that have affected many parts of Pakistan have caused heavy casualties.",
        "The Chinese Foreign Minister has told Pakistani Foreign Minister Bilawal Bhutto that he expresses his deepest condolences to the victims and expresses his sincere condolences to the bereaved families and the injured.",
        "At least 176 people have been killed and 175 injured in rain-related incidents across Pakistan since June 14, the National Disaster and Management Authority said on Friday, with 577 houses destroyed and another 894 collapsed."
      ],
